}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "8WRGAC14.0A1G" and "WRGAC14" ( + PCB manuf. text and '''1330''' date code) is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
This device is using a '''Realtek''' SoC with an integrated single-stream 802.11ac radio ([ftp://ftp2.dlink.com/PRODUCTS/DIR-816L/REVB/DIR-816L_REVB_RELEASENOTES_1.00B09_EN.DOC seems to be RTL8192ER]).
==Links of Interest== [http://www.dlinkmea.com/partner/media/product_item_downloadables/6314-DIR-816L_A1_Datasheet_01%28HQ%29.pdf Datasheet on '''D-Link Middle East & Africa''']
